017package org.tribuo.ensemble;
018
019import com.oracle.labs.mlrg.olcut.util.Pair;
020import org.tribuo.Example;
021import org.tribuo.Excuse;
022import org.tribuo.Output;
023import org.tribuo.Prediction;
024
025import java.util.List;
026import java.util.Map;
027
028/**
029 * An {@link Excuse} which has a List of excuses for each of the ensemble members.
030 */
031public class EnsembleExcuse<T extends Output<T>> extends Excuse<T> {
032
033    private final List<Excuse<T>> innerExcuses;
034
035    public EnsembleExcuse(Example<T> example, Prediction<T> prediction, Map<String,List<Pair<String,Double>>> weights, List<Excuse<T>> innerExcuses) {
036        super(example,prediction,weights);
037        this.innerExcuses = innerExcuses;
038    }
039
040    /**
041     * The individual ensemble member's excuses.
042     * @return The individual excuses.
043     */
044    public List<Excuse<T>> getInnerExcuses() {
045        return innerExcuses;
046    }
047
048}
